Metcon:
“10 Plagues of Panda!”
For time:
1 – Wall Climb
2 – DeadLifts (120/70kg)
3 – Toes to bar
4 – Burpees
5 – WallBall Shots (#10/6)
6 – Ring Dips
7 – Box Jumps
8 – Pullups
9 – Kettlebell Swings (#32/24)
10 – Tripple Unders (x3 doubles or x6 singles)


After completing the first movement go back to 1 and begin again adding a new movement each round. There are 10 total rounds with one new movement being added each round. In example: Do 1 Wall Climb, then 1 Wall Climb + 2 DeadLifts, then 1 Wall Climb + 2 DeadLifts + 3 Toes to bar etc… *
